BeachGuard,is,an,online,system,originally,used,in,Michigan,that,gathers,beach,sampling,data,from,local,health,agencies,BeachGuard,has,since,been,implemented,by,three,other,states,Illinois,Indiana,and,Ohio,The,service,contains,two,main,functionalities,retreiving,beaches,via,query,and,returning,information,on,beach,closures,and,advisories,The,API,uses,RESTful,calls,and,responses,are,formatted,in,XML